Join us for a fun-filled event at Beacon Hill Park (by the bandshell)! Get ready to dance, socialize, and make new friends at our exciting event. Somatic guide, Ruby Sprake, will guide us through a short and simple meditation to help you get out of your head, into your body, and reconnect with your most authentic self. Post meditation we will head into dancing together with lots of opportunity for connection. This event is a great invitation to step outside of your comfort zone while meeting new people who are doing the same. What to expect? a simple short meditation (no experience needed!) dancing and good music (there are no rules or expectations you can dance however feels comfortable to you) opportunities for connection throughout the entire event 1 non alc beverage a great time! What does my $ cover somatic coach/guide helping with supplies 1 non alc beverage (sorry we can't change the price if you choose not to have one!) About the venue located on a grassy area at beacon Hill park
